						<p style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 11.25pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #777777; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">9.1.2 The tasks assigned are not guaranteed to be completed within the duration; extension of the duration of a Session ("Additional Hours") might be required and charged accordingly. In such a case, the Service Provider has the right to reject the Additional Hours. Should the Service Provider accept, Additional Hours will be not deducted from the remaining hours in the Recurring Service but will be counted outside of the Recurring Service.</span></p>
						<p style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 11.25pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #777777; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">9.1.3 Should a Service Provider cancel a Session for whatever reason, and the Platform be unable to find a replacement Service Provider 24 hours before the start of the next Session, the Customer may elect to change the Booking or cancel the Session free of charge.</span></p>
						<p style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 11.25pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #777777; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">9.1.4 WiiCleaner does not guarantee the same Service Provider for a Customer for all Sessions booked by the Customer.</span></p>
