						<p style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 11.25pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #777777; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">(a) the Customer will be charged for the full Session if the Customer cancels or makes changes to the Session within 24 hours before the start of the Session.</span></p>
