						<p style="line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 11.25pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: #777777; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">11.4 In the event that a Service Provider reached the location of the Session, and the Customer is not there to let the Service Provider in and cannot be reached. The Service Provider can leave the location and the Session will be treated as cancelled. The Service Provider shall take a photo of themselves in the location as proof.</span></p>
